Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jaune] Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're lettin' that\Nboy make a fool of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's not just a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ozpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already reincarnated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ozpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby, you--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Hazel] Ozpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- You thought you could hide from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] No, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ozpin is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not sure, but right\Nnow we've got the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not waste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the path to the vault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got your team covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- You wanna get to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to\Nget through all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ren, talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no, no, no, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Weiss, c'mon, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make sure they leave Ruby alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- I told you, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover]\NPlease, let me take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can handle him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- You told me I needed\Nto fight for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover]\NThis is not your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he so upset with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- He didn't tell you my tale, did he, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you looked familiar,\Nto think that evil was inside
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you when our paths first crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood won't be on my\Nhands, it'll be on his.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- What was he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell him, Ozpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him how you killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] Gretchen\NRainart was Hazel's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite her brother's wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she enrolled at Beacon\NAcademy to become a Huntress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and tragically lost her\Nlife on a training mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazel holds me responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Hazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's wounded in a way\Nthat cannot be healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Hazel] You know now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forgive me for\Nwhat I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she know the risk of being a Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- She was only a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- She made a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A choice to put others before herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then you've chosen death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ozpin Voiceover] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ozpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's hardly breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I, I don't know what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, it wasn't supposed to be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't lose anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you nervous, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The first Maiden in, why,\NI'm not sure anyone knows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,how many years is about to open a vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say it's quite an exciting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel honored?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I'm not concerned with any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All I care about is my tribe, my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a burden, not an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've conditioned\Nher quite well, Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's certainly grander than Beacon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the extra effort was for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we please not linger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think she's going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whatever you're doing, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good, Oscar needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jaune and Weiss still need cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- No one's gonna touch 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, make it happen, Ranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Cinder] Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Raven] Vernal, stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, come now, Raven, let her enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Vernal] How does this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Once the Spring Maiden places
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,her hand on the door, it will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, and only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will walk into the\Nvault, and retrieve the Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- It doesn't matter to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Vernal, when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've heard so many\Nstories about you, Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you're a cunning leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're strong, that you're clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Raven] Vernal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's nothing personal, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just not worthy\Nof such power, but I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will take what is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- You won't find it, because\NVernal isn't the Spring Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!!
